How I refresh my natural texture 🍥🪄

 I always opt for a blowout because keeping texture in your hair can mean more work day to day. Having a low maintenance curl refresh routine will make life so much easier in the long run 💆🏽‍♀️ 

I’m first using @kevin.murphy KILLER WAVES mist and spritzing throughout my hair

Then I’m going in with @mykitsch spray bottle to dampen my hair, giving a little extra wetness to my part area 

Lastly I’m taking @kevin.murphy KILLER CURLS crème applying to my part area and scrunching into pieces framing my face

After all products are applied I’m going in with my @oliviagarden_int blow dryer with the diffuser attached 
Turning the air setting down and heat setting up 
Softly diffusing hair till it starts to hold shape and body again 

Haircut & Color @joeyperrotti
